Some future ToDos
=================

 * Better visualization of packets during debug-output
 * Colorize debug output, according to Proto and checksum 
   (e.g. bogus packets with black bg)
 * BPF filter code generation
 * Plugin framework
 * Support for data export in pcap file format
 * Deep Packet Inspection
 * Some more device statistics for wireless net devices
 * Support for setting CPU affinity
 * Regexp on packet content
 * ... 
